Package: publicationFigureRenderer
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - Publication-Ready Pedigree SVG Renderer
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal Evagene REST API integration that fetches a pedigree
    as SVG and optionally replaces display names with publication-safe
    labels (generation-number / initials / off) before writing the SVG to
    disk.  Distributed as an example; not a validated clinical tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0),
    xml2 (>= 1.3.6)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
